        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>The Accuseal double band clamp used between the muffler and exhaust pipe must be installed
                    correctly to assure joint integrity and clamp life. Review the following Service Procedure before
                    installing the Accuseal band clamp.
                </para>
                <specpara>
                    <note>
                        <para>Steps 5, 6 and 7 of this Service Procedure are part of Heavy Duty Pre-Delivery Inspection,
                            Form Number CTS-1197, Exterior Inspection, and needs to be followed in its entirety for
                            clamp life.
                        </para>
                    </note>
                </specpara>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
